WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.752
imetimia kama miaka 10, toka mtikisiko 
wa mwisho wa uchumi

00:00:04.776 --> 00:00:07.102
lakini bado tasnia ni kubwa sana

00:00:07.725 --> 00:00:11.265
Sheria ambazo zilipaswa kusimamia vema 
mashirika makubwa.

00:00:11.289 --> 00:00:12.850
yameishia kuumiza mashirika madogo,

00:00:12.874 --> 00:00:17.945
ikisababisha mali nyingi kudhibitiwa 
na asilimia moja ya juu.

00:00:18.550 --> 00:00:20.144
wamekuwa wakubwa sana kuanguka

00:00:21.386 --> 00:00:23.589
Simaanishi benki kubwa,

00:00:23.613 --> 00:00:26.107
lakini namaanisha ulimwengu 
wa Kilimo Kikubwa.

00:00:27.470 --> 00:00:28.966
Kama mtendaji wa afya ya jamii

00:00:28.990 --> 00:00:31.698
ambaye amefanya kazi na 
wakulima wadogo Rwanda